    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Michel Langeveld</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:284px;\"><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20020113161900/http://www.chessbase.de/events/events.asp?pid=86\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/72/MichelLangeveld.JPG\" width=\"282\" height=\"384\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:MichelLangeveld.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Michel Langeveld operating <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Michel Langeveld</b>,<br />\na Dutch chess player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and computer chess programmer. \nHe is author of the chess program <a href=\"/Nullmover\" title=\"Nullmover\">Nullmover</a>, and in 2004 modified <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a> to play <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gothic_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gothic Chess (page does not exist)\">Gothic Chess</a>, dubbed <a href=\"/index.php?title=TSCP_Gothic&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"TSCP Gothic (page does not exist)\">TSCP Gothic</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \nto play the <i>2004 Gothic Chess Computer World Championship</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\nAt the <a href=\"/WMCCC_2001\" title=\"WMCCC 2001\">WMCCC 2001</a> Michel Langeveld served as <a href=\"/Category:Opening_Book_Author\" title=\"Category:Opening Book Author\">opening book author</a> and operator of <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1999\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1999</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2003\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2003</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2004\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2004</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1999\">1999</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1999\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=57235\">Why did Cray Blitz has a king safety hashtable?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 21, 1999&#160;» <a href=\"/Cray_Blitz\" title=\"Cray Blitz\">Cray Blitz</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=64355\">Re: the KRPP KR challenge. system limits</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 11, 1999</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=129597\">Michel Langeveld is smarter than I am</a> by <a href=\"/Dann_Corbit\" title=\"Dann Corbit\">Dann Corbit</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 15, 2000</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=201147\">Nullmover - Embracer (weird game)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 09, 2001</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=202604\">Leo Dijkman's WBEC</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 19, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/WBEC\" title=\"WBEC\">WBEC</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2003\">2003</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2003\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=304213\">How much ply should FINE #70 be solved?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 02, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Lasker-Reichhelm_Position\" title=\"Lasker-Reichhelm Position\">Fine #70</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=321449\">Fine #70</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 15, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Lasker-Reichhelm_Position\" title=\"Lasker-Reichhelm Position\">Fine #70</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=323799\">Rebel against Nullmover</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2003&#160;» <a href=\"/Rebel\" title=\"Rebel\">Rebel</a>, <a href=\"/DOCCC_2003\" title=\"DOCCC 2003\">DOCCC 2003</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2004\">2004</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2004\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=343651\">To Michael Langeveld</a> by Rick Rice, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 20, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=344036\">Question about details of hashing (olithink)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Michel Langeveld</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2004&#160;» <a href=\"/OliThink\" title=\"OliThink\">OliThink</a>, <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20050213005119/http://www.gothicchess.org/world_comp_champ_2004.html\">2004 Gothic Chess Computer World Championship</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://players.chessbase.com/en/player/Langeveld_Michel/528772\">Michel Langeveld player profile - ChessBase Players</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Michel_Langeveld&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20020113161900/http://www.chessbase.de/events/events.asp?pid=86\">Mikrocomputer Schachweltmeisterschaft 2001, Fotos vom fünften Spieltag</a> by <a href=\"/Eric_van_Reem\" title=\"Eric van Reem\">Eric van Reem</a>, <a href=\"/ChessBase\" title=\"ChessBase\">ChessBase Events</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wayback_Machine\">Wayback Machine</a>)</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://players.chessbase.com/en/player/Langeveld_Michel/528772\">Michel Langeveld player pr